	<td>
		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Warbeads</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><a href="mailto:jam77@thot.net">Jike</a> | 
                        11/25/1999 12:24:36 AM</b></font></p>
			
			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">In Rivervale, talk to Sheriff Roglio in the Guardian Stronghold. He will inform you of a danger. When asked about this danger, he infoms you of the goblin menace. He requests that you bring him any RunnyEye Warbeads. Save those beads!!!! When you bring them back to him, give them one at a time to him. Sometimes you get money and experience (money being some silver pieces). Sometimes he gives you nothing. Keep giving him the beads anyhow. I have been given two large lanterns, one after the other, a dagger, turqouise, and a party member was given a mace!!! The weapons were rusty, but selling them is an option.
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
			</p>
	</td>
		<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
		
