				Curently you only get exp and money for every fourth or fifth warbead you turn in.  So if you don't get anything the first time, keep giving them to him.  He seems to remember how many you have given him so if you give him 3 and don't get anything, then go back later and give him 1 or 2 more, you will get the reward then.  Lately I've been getting the reward consistantly for every 4th bead turned in.<BR>
<BR>
