	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is the quest for the Squad Ring which has a Healing charge on it. It is based on points:<BR>
<BR>
Halflings need 1000 points and non-Halflings need 1500.<BR>
<BR>
Points - <BR>
<BR>
1 for each RunnyEye Warbead turned in.<BR>
1 for each Goblin killed.<BR>
5 for each DeathFist Slashed Belt turned in.<BR>
20 for killing Mooto.<BR>
<BR>
Once you have gained enough faction, talk to the Marshall near the table on the first floor of the castle in Riverale. He will give you the Squad Ring.<BR>
<BR>
*On a side note: Give the Warbeads to Roglio 4 at a time. He will sometimes give armor, lanterns, or bags.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
