				Someone commented on not always getting faction points or goodies when giving warbeads to Roglio. You must give them to him 4 at a time and MUST NOT give him any shattered warbeads, if you do you get nothing and loose the good beads - so be sure to at all your beads first. Shattered ones can usually be sold for about 2 cp. Hope this helps.
